<![CDATA[
<p>Ever wonder how microorganisms affect human, animal, and environmental health? Tiny organisms affect our lives in profound ways. Advances in microbiology have had a great impact in areas such as agriculture, biotechnology, ecology, medicine, and veterinary science.</p>
